    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0

    v0 = wp.exp(wp.exp(wp.sin(v0 + 0.05)))
    tmp = wp.abs((wp.sin(v2 + 0.90) / wp.cos(v0 + 0.10)))
    v2 = v1
    v0 = wp.cos(((tmp + 0.23 * v0 + 0.81) + wp.sin(v2 + 0.66)))
    v1 = (wp.cos((v2 + 0.94 - tmp + 0.69)) / v0)
    v2 = (0.58 - tmp)
    v1 = wp.abs(wp.sin(tmp))
    data[tid] = v0
